00:22:58,440 --> 00:23:00,941
of discovery throughout the park.

506
00:23:00,941 --> 00:23:06,264
How can we extend that to maybe a classic attraction?

507
00:23:06,264 --> 00:23:09,966
So as a pilot to try out what does this look like,

